38855.name: {BC{4a{3t{#h{*ed{#r{3a{Bl Gardens{x
description: Thornbushes line the stairs, gripping your breeches as you pass.
Grudgingly letting you by, the thornbushes give way to the Doors of
the Tomb before you.  Massive pillars rise above you, seamlessly
meeting the arch of the great roof, and marking the great bronze doors
not far before you.  Thunder claps suddenly, booming with the power of
a thousand cannons, and stormclouds darken the sky.  Lightning
flashes...  Once...  Twice...  Three times, each a different shade of
evil.  The doors loom above you, bidding you enter in from the storm.
Bidding you to enter your own {4d{Be{*s{3t{#r{7u{#c{3t{*i{Bo{4n{x.

38851.name: Hall Of Fury
description: Raging winds beat at you from all sides, all but hurling you
against the walls of this small chamber.  The black, even surface of
the walls gleam eerily at you in the darkness, showing the way further
into the furious tombs below.  Exits lie above and to the west.
